  div[style=h1_email]
    |Send us your resume by email
div[style=body_email]
  |You may also send us your resume and we will post it. For that you have to send by #{link_to 'email@jobsgalore.eu', "mailto:email@jobsgalore.eu?subject=The resume for posting on jobsgalore"}:
  div[style=message_email]
    ul
      li
        |Your resume in MS Word 2007(*.docx) format;
      li
